OL,3,CPolice investigate alleged attack on
OL,4,Cprison officer by Southport killer
OL,6,FPolice are investigating an alleged
OL,7,Fattack on a prison officer at HMP
OL,8,FBelmarsh by Southport triple killer
OL,9,FAxel Rudakubana.
OL,11,FThe 18-year-old allegedly used a
OL,12,Fkettle in his cell to heat water up
OL,13,Fand then poured boiling water over the
OL,14,Fofficer on Thursday, the PA news
OL,15,Fagency understands.
OL,17,FThe prison officer was taken to
OL,18,Fhospital as a precautionary measure,
OL,19,Fdid not require further treatment and
OL,20,Fwas discharged later that evening, it
OL,21,Fis understood.
