OL,6,FThey are expected to return to work
OL,7,Fnext week.
OL,9,FRudakubana was jailed for a minimum of
OL,10,F52 years in January for the murders of
OL,11,Fthree girls and attempted murders of
OL,12,Feight other children, class instructor
OL,13,FLeanne Lucas and businessman John
OL,14,FHayes.
OL,16,FThe 18-year-old murdered Alice da
OL,17,FSilva Aguiar, nine, Bebe King, six,
OL,18,Fand Elsie Dot Stancombe, seven, and
OL,19,Finjured 10 others during the attack at
OL,20,Fthe Taylor Swift-themed workshop on
OL,21,FJuly 29 last year.
