OL,3,CPolice investigate alleged attack on
OL,4,Cprison officer by Southport killer
OL,6,FA Prison Service spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Police are investigating an attack on
OL,8,Fa prison officer at HMP Belmarsh
OL,9,Fyesterday.
OL,11,F"Violence in prison will not be
OL,12,Ftolerated and we will always push for
OL,13,Fthe strongest possible punishment for
OL,14,Fattacks on our hardworking staff."
OL,16,FThe Home Secretary said in April that
OL,17,Fan inquiry into the Southport murders
OL,18,Fhad formally begun its work looking at
OL,19,Fhow to learn lessons from the attack.
