OL,6,FShadow justice secretary Robert
OL,7,FJenrick said the alleged attack by
OL,8,FRudakubana was the "third astonishing
OL,9,Fsecurity failure at a top security
OL,10,Fprison".
OL,12,FIn a post on X, Mr Jenrick said:
OL,13,F"Warning after warning has been
OL,14,Fignored.
OL,16,F"I personally raised security at HMP
OL,17,FBelmarsh just last week.
OL,19,F"This is a full blown crisis. No more
OL,20,Flengthy 'reviews' ` the Justice
OL,21,FSecretary needs to act NOW."
