OL,6,FThe number of assaults on staff in
OL,7,Fadult prisons in England and Wales per
OL,8,Fyear has reached its highest level in
OL,9,Fa decade, according to data from the
OL,10,FMinistry of Justice.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FSome 10,605 assaults on staff in male
OL,18,Fand female jails were recorded in
OL,19,F2024, up from 9,204 in 2023 and nearly
OL,20,Fthree times the 3,640 in 2014.
