OL,3,CPolice investigate alleged attack on
OL,4,Cprison officer by Southport killer
OL,6,FFour guards were attacked with hot oil
OL,7,Fand homemade weapons by Manchester
OL,8,FArena bomb plotter Hashem Abedi at HMP
OL,9,FFrankland in County Durham in April,
OL,10,Fwith the inmate transferred to
OL,11,FBelmarsh after the incident.
OL,13,FIn response to the rise in attacks,
OL,14,FJustice Secretary Shabana Mahmood
OL,15,Fpreviously announced that the use of
OL,16,Ftasers will be trialled in prisons and
OL,17,Fconfirmed the Prison Service will
OL,18,Fconduct a "snap review" of the use of
OL,19,Fprotective body armour for prison
OL,20,Fofficers.
